<div class="mainblock">
<h1>Testing PI:image</h1>
 <p>
   Images may be defined in separate images files defined in the script or they may
   be defined when they are used.
</p>
<p>
 In this example there are one file with image definitions, 
 <?_wxt popup lang="lang-xml" sourcelocation="images/someimages.xml" 
        location="images/someimages_xml.html" text="someimages.xml"?>. 
 The rest of the images are defined when used.
</p>
<p>
 Different display modes: 0,1,2,3,4(=default):
</p>
<h3>0</h3>
<div><?_wxt image  id="bs2" removeparent="yes" display="0"?></div>
<h3>1</h3>
<div><?_wxt image  id="bs5"  display="1"?></div>
<h3>2</h3>
<div><?_wxt image  id="bs3"  display="2"?></div>
<h3>3</h3>
<div><?_wxt image  id="bs6"  display="3"?></div>
<h3>4</h3>
<div><?_wxt image  id="bs1"  display="4"?></div>

    
<hr/>
    
<h2>Content file for this page</h2>
<div>
<?_wxt expandable location="welcome.xml" lang="lang-xml"?>
</div>
</div> <!-- mainblock -->

</body>
</html>
